  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to Draw Rider 2 - fun arcade racing games in which both time trips and special missions are waiting for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>- 32 unique and challenging levels (in history and challenge mode)<br>- An infinite number of user levels in online mode<br>- Create your own levels using the built-in editor<br>- Deadly obstacles: spikes, saws, balls, pits and more<br>- Realistic bike physics<br>- Unique walking character physics<br>- The character realistically shatters into pieces with a lot of guts and blood<br>- Several game characters (Max and Emily)<br>- Fun professional character dubbing from Domenick DeFrank<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story Mode:</h2>Discover the incredible story of Max and Emily, which begins with a ordinary bike ride.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=552 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Mode:</h2>The goal is simple - to survive and get to the finish line. This is not so easy to do: deadly traps and obstacles await you everywhere.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor:</h2>Be creative! Built-in level editor is the main feature of Draw Rider 2. Feel yourself an architect and draw a unique track.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=550 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online:</h2>Play on the crazy tracks of other players. Compete, rate and set records!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/c1bb746a338adfe65a4649f381326e4d.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=552 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/c1bb746a338adfe65a4649f381326e4d.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/c1bb746a338adfe65a4649f381326e4d.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/481059969ebeefb5a1290071f4648597.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to Draw Rider 2 - fun arcade racing games in which both time trips and special missions are waiting for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2>- 32 unique and challenging levels (in history and challenge mode)<br>- An infinite number of user levels in online mode<br>- Create your own levels using the built-in editor<br>- Deadly obstacles: spikes, saws, balls, pits and more<br>- Realistic bike physics<br>- Unique walking character physics<br>- The character realistically shatters into pieces with a lot of guts and blood<br>- Several game characters (Max and Emily)<br>- Fun professional character dubbing from Domenick DeFrank<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story Mode:</h2>Discover the incredible story of Max and Emily, which begins with a ordinary bike ride.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=552 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/fecea51140c036e199646c26d42a7e04.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Mode:</h2>The goal is simple - to survive and get to the finish line. This is not so easy to do: deadly traps and obstacles await you everywhere.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/f1b72f41d5926c62244f2ded23bf8308.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor:</h2>Be creative! Built-in level editor is the main feature of Draw Rider 2. Feel yourself an architect and draw a unique track.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=550 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.webm?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/b9419dd22a020573f3e553a43a6950c5.mp4?t=1731404964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online:</h2>Play on the crazy tracks of other players. Compete, rate and set records!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588630/extras/c1bb746a338adfe65a4649f381326e4d.poster.avif?t=1731404964\" width=552 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared